Combine @mayonnaise{1/2%cup}, @ketchup{1/2%cup}, @yellow mustard{1/4%cup}, @sweet pickle relish{2%Tbsps}, @white pepper{1/2%tsp}, @garlic powder{1/4%tsp}, @Hungarian paprika{1/2%tsp}, @coriander{1/2%tsp}, @apple cider vinegar{1%tsp}, and @Worcestershire sauce{1/2%tsp} in a #mixing bowl{} and #whisk{} together.

This sauce recipe is created for hamburgers, but it makes a great salad dressing too.
